  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The use of electrocautery for surgical skin incision in general surgery is known to decrease
      post-operative pain. This study compares the use of scalpel and electrocautery for surgical
      skin incision in open carpal tunnel release (OCTR).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
